_sText:
de_kolsch is a port of the dod_kolsch map from Day of Defeat: Source game.

dod_kolsch is a map made in 2008 that looks and plays really great!

It is a wonderful example of what can be done with map customization taken right up to its playable limits. 

This is one of those maps that are just so packed with unique 'stuff' that one must wander around it for a while by themselves to take it all in. 

- Now this map is adapted for plant a bomb by terrorists.
